-- Lakshmi Mittal appointed CEO of Arcelor Mittal
-- 
-- Mon Nov 6, 2006 2:17am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/06/us-minerals-mittal-ceo-idUSWEB048620061106

 

 AMSTERDAM  (Reuters) - Steel group Arcelor Mittal MTBL.BR CELR.PA said on Monday it is appointing Lakshmi Mittal, chief executive officer Mittal, as CEO of the combined entity, replacing Roland Junck. 

 "We are making these changes to clarify the leadership of the company," Arcelor Mittal's board chairman Joseph Kinsch said in a statement.